# CODEOWNERS file for Infrastructure Repository
# This file defines who must review changes before they are merged

# Rule 1: Default owners for the whole repository
# If no specific rule matches, these owners will review the change
* @infra-owner @infra-backup

# Rule 2: Core infrastructure configuration
# Changes that affect shared or base infrastructure setup
/config/ @infra-owner

# Rule 3: Environment-related files
# Files that belong to different environments such as dev or production
/environments/ @env-owner
